==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tamis
<hw>Tam"is</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., a kind of
sieve.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A sieve, or strainer, made of a kind of
woolen cloth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The cloth itself; tammy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Tamis bird</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>a Guinea
fowl.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tamkin</ent>⟦br⟧
